    <![endif]-->
  </head>

  <body>

    <div class="container">

      <div class="blog-header">
        <h1 class="blog-title">Whoops!</h1>
        <p class="lead blog-description"><%= msg %></p>
      </div>

      <div class="row">

        <div class="col-sm-3 col-sm-offset-1 blog-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-module sidebar-module-inset">
            <h4>About</h4>
            <p>The Watch Trump Blog takes a screenshot every time President Donald Trump sends out a tweet. It was written by Stephen Mayeux, a software developer in Austin, TX.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sidebar-module">
            <h4>Get In Touch</h4>
            <ol class="list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="https://github.com/StephenMayeux" target="_blank">GitHub</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://twitter.com/eslHipHop" target="_blank">Twitter</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.thebestjs.com" target="_blank">Learn To Code</a></li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div><!-- /.blog-sidebar -->

      </div><!-- /.row -->

    </div><!-- /.container -->

    <footer class="blog-footer">
      <p>We must not confuse dissent with disloyalty. When the loyal opposition dies, I think the soul of America dies with it.</p>
      <p><em>&mdash; Edward R. Murrow</em></p>
    </footer>


